summary: This is a certified copy of a birth certificate issued by the General Register Office on October 15, 2021. It appears to be entered as a government exhibit (Exhibit 16) in a legal proceeding, but the specific details of the child and parents are redacted.

events.title: Certification of Birth Certificate Copy
events.description: The General Register Office certified a copy of a birth certificate under its seal.

keyFacts: This document is a certified copy of a birth certificate, designated as Government Exhibit 16.
The certification was issued by the General Register Office on October 15, 2021.
All identifying information (child's name, date/place of birth, parents' names and details) is redacted or not filled in on the provided text.
The document includes a caution about offences relating to falsifying certificates and a warning that a certificate is not evidence of identity.
The document reference EFTA00088944 and exhibit number suggest it was entered into evidence in a legal case, likely related to the Epstein investigation.
